            "endSeconds": 9506,
            "summary": "Advocated for retaining the in-house district mental health counseling team, emphasizing the critical support counselors provide and the relationships they have built with students over time."
          },
          {
            "name": "Maria Stockton",
            "startSeconds": 9520,
            "endSeconds": 9718,
            "summary": "As CSEA representative, criticized the timing and process of the cuts, urged board members to visit school sites to understand affected staff roles, and objected to positions being fully eliminated rather than simply reduced."
