          {
            "name": "Jessica Shade",
            "startSeconds": 9833,
            "endSeconds": 9925,
            "summary": "Announced a citizens initiative effort to place a parcel tax on the ballot to counteract budget cuts and directed community members to www.strongschools4rwc.org to get involved."
